ion provides safety rails. First sprint: add a value_score computed column to the _ret_ids temp table collection step and sort purge candidates by ascending value score.\",\"reasoning\":\"Fixed retention windows treat a one-cent test run and a fifty-dollar multi-hour execution identically. The retention pipeline already touches every row via the batched index scan, so computing a value heuristic adds minimal overhead. This is a genuinely novel capability: no AI orchestration platform offers value-aware data lifecycle management. It turns retention from a cost center into a strategic advantage.\",\"status\":\"pending\",\"user_feedback\":null,\"user_pattern\":0,\"effort\":6,\"impact\":8,\"implemented_at\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-18T11:48:42.101Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-18T11:48:42.101Z\",\"requirement_id\":null,\"goal_id\":null,\"risk\":5,\"provider\":null,\"model\":null,\"detailed\":0}}\n{\"idea\":{\"id\":\"ae913a95-8128-4e97-80fc-2ea0bae69a22\",\"scan_id\":\"5f014f2a-1ad2-4f4f-8152-28198e0297c3\",\"project_id\":\"c6fd0474-19f1-4223-b6a9-752077c51d3d\",\"context_id\":null,\"scan_type\":\"moonshot_architect\",\"category\":\"functionality\",\"title\":\"Live Execution Metrics via Kafka Event Stream\",\"description\":\"Eliminate the 24-hour metrics blind spot by publishing execution completion events to Kafka in real-time, enabling live dashboards and instant alerting. Currently metrics only materialize during the daily retention aggregation. Emit a lightweight metrics event on every execution status change through the existing Kafka infrastructure (kafkaEnabled is already configured). Build a real-time metrics table with minute-level granularity alongside the daily rollup. First sprint: add a Kafka producer call in updateExecution when status transitions to completed/failed, publishing persona_id, cost_usd, duration_ms, and status.\",\"reasoning\":\"The Kafka infrastructure already exists but is used only for event dispatching. The daily retention aggregation creates a massive observability gap where operators fly blind for up to 24 hours. Real-time metrics streaming transforms personas-cloud from a batch-analytics system into a live operations platform. Combined with per-tenant isolation, this creates the foundation for SLA monitoring, auto-scaling triggers, and real-time cost controls.\",\"status\":\"pending\",\"user_feedback\":null,\"user_pattern\":0,\"effort\":7,\"impact\":10,\"implemented_at\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-18T11:48:42.129Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-18T11:48:42.129Z\",\"requirement_id\":null,\"goal_id\":null,\"risk\":6,\"provider\":null,\"model\":null,\"detailed\":0}}","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
